The management of the National Youth Service Corps (NYSC) has said that based on their records, it was revealed that the Federal Minister of Finance, Mrs Kemi Adeosun actually applied for an Exemption Certificate. In a statement signed by the Director, Press and Publications Relations, Mrs. Adenike Adeyemi, the scheme will investigate the origin of the purported Exemption Certificate in question. The scheme is yet to reveal if she was actually given the exemption certificate which she applied for.